Subject: [PATCH v2 05/19] drm: Allow the caller to pass in the format info to
 drm_helper_mode_fill_fb_struct()
Date: Tue,  1 Jul 2025 12:07:08 +0300
Message-ID: <20250701090722.13645-6-ville.syrjala@linux.intel.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.49.0
In-Reply-To: <20250701090722.13645-1-ville.syrjala@linux.intel.com>
References: <20250701090722.13645-1-ville.syrjala@linux.intel.com>
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
X-BeenThere: dri-devel@lists.freedesktop.org
